title: PERSON OF INTEREST S3 GAG REEL
author: CatchWitt

Shahi has hardcore straight face skills.

book drops on Finch's head 
"oww.."
ITS SO FREAKING CUTE OMG
The best part is when I can't get out of the taxi
"Everything I have I owe to spaghetti"
